title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Sex, Drugs and Grime
description:
Happy new year, Throw Gang! The ballots are in and the results have been tabulated. To celebrate the end of the most ass year in history, Jimmy and Larry are linking up IRL to reveal, analyze and break down the best of 2020, as voted by you in the 1st annual The Fitties.
